Invocation Name: daily doggo
des:
Want to learn more about Dog Breeds? This is the skill for you! Every day of the year you will receive a different dog breed with a short description straight from WIkipedia. You can also ask for additional breeds if one a day isn't enough for you.

------------------------------------------
Changelog 12-17
- Sped up response time significantly
- Fixed breeds with blank responses
- Implemented shorter responses and ability to ask for more
- Skill no longer exits on one intent
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
